                            <comment id="13911040" author="xuefuz" created="Tue, 25 Feb 2014 00:31:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The regression was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-1367&quot; title=&quot;cluster by multiple columns does not work if parenthesis is present&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-1367&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-1367&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. SQL standard &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; grammar for order by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;         &amp;lt;order by clause&amp;gt; ::=
              ORDER BY &amp;lt;sort specification list&amp;gt;

         &amp;lt;sort specification list&amp;gt; ::=
              &amp;lt;sort specification&amp;gt; [ { &amp;lt;comma&amp;gt; &amp;lt;sort specification&amp;gt; }... ]

         &amp;lt;sort specification&amp;gt; ::=
              &amp;lt;sort key&amp;gt; [ &amp;lt;collate clause &amp;gt; ] [ &amp;lt;ordering specification&amp;gt; ]

         &amp;lt;sort key&amp;gt; ::=
                &amp;lt;column name&amp;gt;
              | &amp;lt;unsigned integer&amp;gt;

         &amp;lt;ordering specification&amp;gt; ::= ASC | DESC
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the standard we can see that , order by clause doesn&apos;t not need `(` and `)` to enclose the sorted columns. However, hive allows an expression in lieu of a column name in the sorted column list, and &apos;(&apos; and &apos;)&apos; are part of expression. Thus, parenthesis should be interpreted as an expression construct rather than the order_by construct. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The proposal is to remove them from order_by construct.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/~shadow/sql/sql1992.txt&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/~shadow/sql/sql1992.txt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
