                                                                                            <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>From 0.10.0 to 0.13.0, the following syntax for order by is allowed (though the doc doesn&amp;#39;t specify):&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
select * from table order by (expr1, exp2);&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
From 0.14, the above syntax is illegal. Instead, the following should be used:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
select * from table order by expr1, exp2;&lt;br/&gt;
</customfieldvalue>

                        </customfieldvalues>
